highlights.text: “เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1219 days straight.
“BOSS IN THE BUILDING” by BUS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #115.
Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “กุหลาบ” is the highest at #21.
“จากกันด้วยดี (Ordinary)” by Tilly Birds is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 48 spots at #113.
